<font color="#ffff80">Gloria.</font>

197
00:17:30,251 --> 00:17:32,293
<font color="#ffff80">...Gave us these papers.</font>

198
00:17:33,084 --> 00:17:35,084
<font color="#ffff80">We might find something,
and we might not.</font>

199
00:17:36,709 --> 00:17:39,876
<font color="#ffff80">Of course we tried
to find you first,</font>

200
00:17:40,043 --> 00:17:41,376
<font color="#ffff80">but you weren't home,</font>

201
00:17:41,918 --> 00:17:44,418
<font color="#ffff80">so we called your mobile.</font>

202
00:17:44,959 --> 00:17:46,959
<font color="#ffff80">Gloria gave us your number.</font>

203
00:17:47,501 --> 00:17:51,168
<font color="#ffff80">I went out for some painkillers,
my head was about to explode.</font>

204
00:17:53,376 --> 00:17:54,709
<font color="#ffff80">Feeling any better?</font>

205
00:17:55,501 --> 00:17:57,084
<font color="#ffff80">Yes. Thanks a lot.</font>

206
00:18:00,293 --> 00:18:02,084
<font color="#ffff80">Dr. Tapia's here.</font>

207
00:18:07,918 --> 00:18:09,584
<font color="#ffff80">We'll be right back.</font>

208
00:18:34,251 --> 00:18:35,084
<font color="#ffff80">Yes?</font>

209
00:18:35,251 --> 00:18:36,751
<font color="#ffff80">Why didn't you pick up?</font>

210
00:18:36,918 --> 00:18:40,168
<font color="#ffff80">I'm sorry, I thought the
police might have your mobile.</font>

211
00:18:40,334 --> 00:18:42,209
<font color="#ffff80">Nobody took my mobile.
Everything's fine.</font>

212
00:18:42,376 --> 00:18:43,293
<font color="#ffff80">Has she turned up?</font>

213
00:18:43,459 --> 00:18:45,543
<font color="#ffff80">No, but she will. I need
you to do something.</font>

214
00:18:45,709 --> 00:18:47,376
<font color="#ffff80">What do you want me to do?</font>

215
00:18:47,543 --> 00:18:49,959
<font color="#ffff80">The guard saw something,
ran away and got run over.</font>

216
00:18:50,126 --> 00:18:51,793
<font color="#ffff80">He's unconscious
in Intensive Care.</font>

217
00:18:51,959 --> 00:18:55,084
<font color="#ffff80">The police say they don't know what
he saw, but I don't trust them.</font>

218
00:18:55,251 --> 00:18:56,918
<font color="#ffff80">Do you know anyone
at Sacred Heart?</font>

219
00:18:57,251 --> 00:18:58,834
<font color="#ffff80">Alex, what are you asking?</font>

220
00:18:59,001 --> 00:19:01,334
<font color="#ffff80">The guard's there. Do you
know someone or not?</font>

221
00:19:01,501 --> 00:19:03,334
<font color="#ffff80">I did practicals
there last year.</font>

222
00:19:03,501 --> 00:19:06,793
<font color="#ffff80">Go there and find out what you can
without raising any suspicion.</font>

223
00:19:06,959 --> 00:19:09,334
<font color="#ffff80">Can't you go? You must
know people at their lab.</font>

224
00:19:09,501 --> 00:19:10,793
<font color="#ffff80">I can't move from here.</font>

225
00:19:12,001 --> 00:19:14,626
<font color="#ffff80">- Are you under arrest?
- Of course not.</font>

226
00:19:14,793 --> 00:19:18,293
<font color="#ffff80">But they want to question me. I'll
call when I can. Love you. Ciao.</font>

227
00:19:18,459 --> 00:19:19,418
<font color="#ffff80">I love you t...</font>

228
00:19:33,959 --> 00:19:35,918
<font color="#ffff80">You can't smoke here.</font>

229
00:19:36,376 --> 00:19:38,793
<font color="#ffff80">In this situation can't
you turn a blind eye?</font>

230
00:19:39,334 --> 00:19:41,418
<font color="#ffff80">The forensic wants
to talk to you.</font>

231
00:19:42,459 --> 00:19:44,959
<font color="#ffff80">In your statement you say</font>

232
00:19:45,126 --> 00:19:48,126
<font color="#ffff80">your wife returned from L.A. this morning.
Is that right?</font>

233
00:19:48,293 --> 00:19:51,043
<font color="#ffff80">- Yes. A business trip.
- I see she had a fear of flying.</font>

234
00:19:51,209 --> 00:19:54,168
<font color="#ffff80">She'd done various therapies.
Why?</font>

235
00:19:55,001 --> 00:19:58,209
<font color="#ffff80">Stress on long flights can
cause cardiac arrest.</font>

236
00:19:59,834 --> 00:20:02,293
<font color="#ffff80">You think Mayka had a cardiac
because of the trip?</font>

237
00:20:02,626 --> 00:20:04,418
<font color="#ffff80">There is that possibility.</font>

238
00:20:04,584 --> 00:20:08,584
<font color="#ffff80">Though we have no record of
any cardiovascular hazard.</font>

239
00:20:08,751 --> 00:20:10,959
<font color="#ffff80">Perhaps it wasn't detected.</font>

240
00:20:11,126 --> 00:20:14,251
<font color="#ffff80">I don't know, you're the expert.</font>

241
00:20:15,084 --> 00:20:18,668
<font color="#ffff80">Mayka thought she was invincible.
Perhaps that takes its toll.</font>

242
00:20:21,834 --> 00:20:22,668
<font color="#ffff80">Perhaps.</font>

243
00:20:28,793 --> 00:20:31,709
<font color="#ffff80">But without an autopsy
it's impossible to verify.</font>

244
00:20:32,209 --> 00:20:34,084
<font color="#ffff80">Any schizophrenic episode?</font>

245
00:20:35,168 --> 00:20:35,876
<font color="#ffff80">No.</font>

246
00:20:36,043 --> 00:20:37,793
<font color="#ffff80">- Parkinson's?
- Not that either.</font>

247
00:20:37,959 --> 00:20:38,918
<font color="#ffff80">Epilepsy?</font>

248
00:20:39,084 --> 00:20:41,501
<font color="#ffff80">It's all in her medical file.
I don't get it.</font>

249
00:20:41,668 --> 00:20:44,543
<font color="#ffff80">The doctors didn't live with her.
You did.</font>

250
00:20:44,709 --> 00:20:47,543
<font color="#ffff80">I don't get what this has to do
with my wife's disappearance.</font>

251
00:20:48,626 --> 00:20:51,543
<font color="#ffff80">I'd like to rule out a theory
that'd explain what happened.</font>

252
00:20:52,959 --> 00:20:54,084
<font color="#ffff80">What?</font>

253
00:20:55,334 --> 00:20:56,626
<font color="#ffff80">Catalepsy.</font>

254
00:20:56,793 --> 00:20:58,293
<font color="#ffff80">What did you say?</font>

255
00:21:07,084 --> 00:21:08,293
<font color="#ffff80">Alright, Silvia...</font>

256
00:21:08,459 --> 00:21:12,001
<font color="#ffff80">Do you really think it's possible
the corpse wasn't a corpse?</font>

257
00:21:12,168 --> 00:21:14,959
<font color="#ffff80">I certified her death and
I did my job properly,</font>

258
00:21:15,126 --> 00:21:17,626
<font color="#ffff80">but circumstances force me
to reconsider everything.</font>

259
00:21:17,793 --> 00:21:19,751
<font color="#ffff80">It makes no sense.
If she woke up,</font>

260
00:21:19,918 --> 00:21:22,334
<font color="#ffff80">why not cry out for help?
Why disappear?</font>

261
00:21:22,501 --> 00:21:25,668
<font color="#ffff80">He's right. It's more logical
that someone came for her.</font>

262
00:21:25,834 --> 00:21:28,209
<font color="#ffff80">And from a medical
viewpoint, more probable.</font>

263
00:21:28,376 --> 00:21:31,959
<font color="#ffff80">Then let's return to the 21st century
and assume that the cause of death</font>

264
00:21:32,126 --> 00:21:35,251
<font color="#ffff80">was heart attack, as in
your preliminary report.</font>

265
00:21:35,418 --> 00:21:38,918
<font color="#ffff80">The question is: why
was the body taken?</font>

266
00:21:40,126 --> 00:21:43,043
<font color="#ffff80">There's a principle
in forensic medicine:</font>

267
00:21:43,584 --> 00:21:46,918
<font color="#ffff80">"Every death is a homicide
until proven otherwise."</font>

268
00:21:47,834 --> 00:21:49,751
<font color="#ffff80">Cardiac arrest can be induced</font>

269
00:21:49,918 --> 00:21:52,376
<font color="#ffff80">by submitting a person
to extreme tension.</font>

270
00:21:52,709 --> 00:21:56,293
<font color="#ffff80">Or administering substances
that have the same result.</font>

271
00:21:57,126 --> 00:21:59,543
<font color="#ffff80">But nothing's demonstrable
without an autopsy.</font>

272
00:22:00,001 --> 00:22:02,209
<font color="#ffff80">And no body, no autopsy.</font>

273
00:22:11,209 --> 00:22:13,626
<font color="#ffff80">What did you think
when you spoke to him?</font>

274
00:22:13,959 --> 00:22:17,376
<font color="#ffff80">I was surprised how he
referred to his wife.</font>

275
00:22:17,834 --> 00:22:20,918
<font color="#ffff80">He spoke about her in the
past, with no hesitation.</font>

276
00:22:21,376 --> 00:22:23,876
<font color="#ffff80">Ruth died several years ago...</font>

277
00:22:24,668 --> 00:22:27,668
<font color="#ffff80">and I still talk about her
as if she were alive.</font>

278
00:22:32,251 --> 00:22:34,376
<font color="#ffff80">His wife died this afternoon.</font>

279
00:22:36,168 --> 00:22:38,376
<font color="#ffff80">I'll find out
everything about him.</font>

280
00:22:56,959 --> 00:22:59,709
<font color="#ffff80">I'm sorry you had to come
at this time of night.</font>

281
00:23:01,668 --> 00:23:03,501
<font color="#ffff80">And in this weather.</font>

282
00:23:03,876 --> 00:23:06,626
<font color="#ffff80">Pablo tells me you came
back from a trip today,</font>

283
00:23:06,793 --> 00:23:08,376
<font color="#ffff80">to see Eva.</font>

284
00:23:11,876 --> 00:23:13,334
<font color="#ffff80">I hope she's alright.</font>

285
00:23:13,501 --> 00:23:15,043
<font color="#ffff80">She's fine.</font>

286
00:23:15,209 --> 00:23:16,793
<font color="#ffff80">Or seems to be at least.</font>

287
00:23:17,751 --> 00:23:19,084
<font color="#ffff80">And you?</font>

288
00:23:20,418 --> 00:23:22,001
<font color="#ffff80">How are you?</font>

289
00:23:22,626 --> 00:23:24,251
<font color="#ffff80">They told you everything.</font>

290
00:23:25,084 --> 00:23:27,251
<font color="#ffff80">I heard you were
suspended again,</font>

291
00:23:27,959 --> 00:23:29,501
<font color="#ffff80">you went into therapy again...</font>

292
00:23:29,668 --> 00:23:31,418
<font color="#ffff80">I fell off the wagon.</font>

293
00:23:32,459 --> 00:23:34,501
<font color="#ffff80">But I only drink coffee now.</font>

294
00:23:34,668 --> 00:23:37,918
<font color="#ffff80">7 months on coffee, I'm
a gourmet about it.</font>

295
00:23:38,293 --> 00:23:40,418
<font color="#ffff80">Try switching to teas.</font>

296
00:23:41,001 --> 00:23:42,584
<font color="#ffff80">Your heart will thank you.</font>

297
00:23:42,751 --> 00:23:45,584
<font color="#ffff80">My heart's withstood much worse.</font>

298
00:23:47,084 --> 00:23:50,376
<font color="#ffff80">You'd be doing yourself a favour
if you put it behind you.</font>

299
00:23:50,543 --> 00:23:52,876
<font color="#ffff80">When will you stop
blaming yourself?</font>

300
00:23:53,043 --> 00:23:54,876
<font color="#ffff80">It's been a long time.</font>

301
00:23:56,626 --> 00:23:58,751
<font color="#ffff80">It was a night like tonight.</font>

302
00:24:04,251 --> 00:24:06,293
<font color="#ffff80">I'm alone now, Silvia.</font>

303
00:24:08,793 --> 00:24:09,793
<font color="#ffff80">No.</font>

304
00:24:12,251 --> 00:24:13,668
<font color="#ffff80">You're not.</font>

305
00:24:24,876 --> 00:24:26,251
<font color="#ffff80">What's wrong?</font>

306
00:24:26,918 --> 00:24:29,793
<font color="#ffff80">- Where is everyone?
- Go back inside.</font>

307
00:24:29,959 --> 00:24:31,709
<font color="#ffff80">- Have you seen the time?
- Yeah.</font>

308
00:24:31,876 --> 00:24:34,376
<font color="#ffff80">- You know what a day I've had?
- We're working on...</font>

309
00:24:34,543 --> 00:24:38,084
<font color="#ffff80">Listen, please. Tell your
boss I want to go home.</font>

310
00:24:38,293 --> 00:24:39,876
<font color="#ffff80">Be patient.</font>

311
00:24:44,876 --> 00:24:46,459
<font color="#ffff80">I'll see what's happening.</font>

312
00:24:47,834 --> 00:24:49,418
<font color="#ffff80">Please, call your boss.</font>

313
00:24:49,584 --> 00:24:52,293
<font color="#ffff80">Please, Mr. Ulloa, go
back into the office.</font>

314
00:24:52,709 --> 00:24:54,001
<font color="#ffff80">Thank you.</font>

315
00:27:28,251 --> 00:27:29,501
<font color="#ffff80">Mayka.</font>

316
00:27:34,626 --> 00:27:35,918
<font color="#ffff80">Thanks.</font>

317
00:27:38,418 --> 00:27:39,834
<font color="#ffff80">What about yours?</font>

318
00:27:40,626 --> 00:27:43,626
<font color="#ffff80">- It's 9 in the morning.
- Not in Los Angeles.</font>

319
00:27:44,334 --> 00:27:47,084
<font color="#ffff80">And I want to toast to
the trip's success.</font>

320
00:27:48,793 --> 00:27:50,084
<font color="#ffff80">And...</font>

321
00:27:51,334 --> 00:27:52,834
<font color="#ffff80">...to my return.</font>

322
00:28:02,543 --> 00:28:05,209
<font color="#ffff80">- Will this toast do you?
- No.</font>

323
00:28:06,043 --> 00:28:08,918
<font color="#ffff80">The lab called, I have to go.</font>

324
00:28:10,209 --> 00:28:11,501
<font color="#ffff80">Alex...</font>

325
00:28:12,418 --> 00:28:16,126
<font color="#ffff80">We've been apart for 3 weeks.
We have to talk.</font>

326
00:28:16,626 --> 00:28:17,793
<font color="#ffff80">I've got a meeting.</font>

327
00:28:20,418 --> 00:28:23,584
<font color="#ffff80">You're the Director, you
can do what you like.</font>

328
00:28:23,751 --> 00:28:25,418
<font color="#ffff80">No one can fire you.</font>

329
00:28:27,376 --> 00:28:29,209
<font color="#ffff80">Except me.</font>

330
00:28:30,251 --> 00:28:31,959
<font color="#ffff80">You know something?</font>

331
00:28:32,376 --> 00:28:34,501
<font color="#ffff80">I don't like this kind of joke.</font>

332
00:28:34,876 --> 00:28:38,126
<font color="#ffff80">I work hard because I take
what I do very seriously.</font>

333
00:28:38,334 --> 00:28:40,168
<font color="#ffff80">And I do it because I like it.</font>

334
00:28:41,001 --> 00:28:42,168
<font color="#ffff80">I know.</font>

335
00:28:43,001 --> 00:28:47,293
<font color="#ffff80">That's why you're where you are,
and not teaching at a college.</font>

336
00:28:47,876 --> 00:28:49,501
<font color="#ffff80">I don't want to leave angry.</font>

337
00:28:52,209 --> 00:28:53,709
<font color="#ffff80">See you later, okay?</font>

338
00:29:38,918 --> 00:29:40,668
<font color="#ffff80">Hello. Cristina?</font>

339
00:29:41,251 --> 00:29:44,251
<font color="#ffff80">Please call and tell them
Alex can't make the meeting.</font>

340
00:29:45,001 --> 00:29:47,001
<font color="#ffff80">No, he's fine.</font>

341
00:29:47,126 --> 00:29:48,876
<font color="#ffff80">Mayka... What are you doing?</font>

342
00:29:48,959 --> 00:29:51,918
<font color="#ffff80">What's more, he won't be
returning to the lab.</font>

343
00:29:52,084 --> 00:29:53,543
<font color="#ffff80">Get a letter of dismissal
ready for him.</font>

344
00:29:53,626 --> 00:29:54,876
<font color="#ffff80">Mayka... Mayka!</font>

345
00:29:55,293 --> 00:29:56,418
<font color="#ffff80">Of course!</font>

346
00:29:56,584 --> 00:29:59,251
<font color="#ffff80">- What are you doing?
- Of course I'm serious.</font>

347
00:29:59,418 --> 00:30:02,834
<font color="#ffff80">It's my company. It's my
decision and I've just made it.</font>

348
00:30:03,501 --> 00:30:04,918
<font color="#ffff80">Thanks.</font>

349
00:30:09,001 --> 00:30:10,793
<font color="#ffff80">We'll sort it out
this afternoon,</font>

350
00:30:10,959 --> 00:30:14,084
<font color="#ffff80">but now we have the whole
morning to ourselves.</font>

351
00:30:14,251 --> 00:30:15,376
<font color="#ffff80">Come here...</font>

352
00:30:16,459 --> 00:30:17,668
<font color="#ffff80">Alex?</font>

353
00:30:24,084 --> 00:30:25,293
<font color="#ffff80">Darling!</font>

354
00:30:25,834 --> 00:30:27,584
<font color="#ffff80">I didn't speak to anyone!</font>

355
00:30:29,126 --> 00:30:31,084
<font color="#ffff80">You're like a child.</font>

356
00:30:35,334 --> 00:30:38,251
<font color="#ffff80">I'll book a table somewhere
for dinner when you get out.</font>

357
00:30:41,001 --> 00:30:42,834
<font color="#ffff80">You'll be sleepy...</font>

358
00:30:44,043 --> 00:30:45,543
<font color="#ffff80">from the jet lag.</font>

359
00:30:45,876 --> 00:30:47,709
<font color="#ffff80">I'll be awake.</font>

360
00:30:48,334 --> 00:30:50,501
<font color="#ffff80">Tell me when you want the table.</font>

361
00:30:51,668 --> 00:30:53,209
<font color="#ffff80">Tonight...</font>

362
00:30:54,876 --> 00:30:57,084
<font color="#ffff80">Tonight you will be mine.</font>

363
00:31:08,209 --> 00:31:10,709
<font color="#ffff80">- Why'd you leave the office?
- What are you doing here?</font>

364
00:31:11,376 --> 00:31:13,626
<font color="#ffff80">I heard a noise.</font>

365
00:31:14,001 --> 00:31:17,251
<font color="#ffff80">The fuses blew, but
it's fixed now.</font>

366
00:31:17,668 --> 00:31:18,709
<font color="#ffff80">What...?</font>

367
00:31:21,459 --> 00:31:24,459
<font color="#ffff80">It's the box with the
deceased's personal items.</font>

368
00:31:26,376 --> 00:31:28,001
<font color="#ffff80">They were in this locker.</font>

369
00:31:32,584 --> 00:31:34,376
<font color="#ffff80">The lock's been jimmied.</font>

370
00:31:36,584 --> 00:31:38,876
<font color="#ffff80">Were you searching through
your wife's things?</font>

371
00:31:39,043 --> 00:31:41,084
<font color="#ffff80">No, I didn't touch anything.</font>

372
00:31:41,251 --> 00:31:45,626
<font color="#ffff80">According to the delivery note,
the mobile phone's missing.</font>

373
00:31:46,293 --> 00:31:47,626
<font color="#ffff80">It was in here.</font>

374
00:31:48,001 --> 00:31:49,543
<font color="#ffff80">I didn't take anything.</font>

375
00:31:49,709 --> 00:31:51,418
<font color="#ffff80">Who was it then?</font>

376
00:31:51,584 --> 00:31:52,876
<font color="#ffff80">One of the dead?</font>

377
00:31:53,043 --> 00:31:55,793
<font color="#ffff80">They got bored and wanted
to liven up our night?</font>

378
00:31:56,293 --> 00:31:58,168
<font color="#ffff80">Empty your pockets.</font>

379
00:32:01,209 --> 00:32:03,709
<font color="#ffff80">Why would I take
my wife's mobile?</font>

380
00:32:08,001 --> 00:32:09,709
<font color="#ffff80">Please, Mr. Ulloa.</font>

381
00:32:14,376 --> 00:32:16,876
<font color="#ffff80">Incredible. Incredible.</font>

382
00:32:28,168 --> 00:32:29,584
<font color="#ffff80">MY Phone.</font>

383
00:32:30,543 --> 00:32:31,876
<font color="#ffff80">Thanks.</font>

384
00:32:34,043 --> 00:32:34,876
<font color="#ffff80">Is that it?</font>

385
00:32:41,959 --> 00:32:43,501
<font color="#ffff80">Arms up.</font>

386
00:32:45,709 --> 00:32:48,418
<font color="#ffff80">- What?
- Do as I say.</font>

387
00:32:49,168 --> 00:32:50,793
<font color="#ffff80">- Why?
- I'm going to search you.</font>

388
00:32:50,959 --> 00:32:52,001
<font color="#ffff80">No.</font>

389
00:32:52,459 --> 00:32:54,709
<font color="#ffff80">- Turn around.
- You've got no right.</font>

390
00:32:54,876 --> 00:32:56,293
<font color="#ffff80">Turn around! Fuck!</font>

391
00:32:57,793 --> 00:33:01,376
<font color="#ffff80">What is this? What?</font>

392
00:33:01,543 --> 00:33:04,751
<font color="#ffff80">- You've got no right.
- Fucking turn around!</font>

393
00:33:04,918 --> 00:33:05,543
<font color="#ffff80">Jaime!</font>

394
00:33:28,251 --> 00:33:29,084
<font color="#ffff80">What's this?</font>

395
00:33:29,459 --> 00:33:31,793
<font color="#ffff80">It was on the floor. I was
going to throw it out.</font>

396
00:33:31,959 --> 00:33:34,501
<font color="#ffff80">No recycling? That's not nice.</font>

397
00:33:36,001 --> 00:33:37,918
