01:09:04,376 --> 01:09:07,209
<font color="#ffff80">your wife died of cardiac arrest.
Do you think I'm an idiot?</font>

795
01:09:07,376 --> 01:09:09,043
<font color="#ffff80">Do you think I'm an idiot?</font>

796
01:09:09,584 --> 01:09:11,418
<font color="#ffff80">I didn't poison my wife.</font>

797
01:09:11,584 --> 01:09:15,043
<font color="#ffff80">If I did, I wouldn't come here
with a vial of the toxin.</font>

798
01:09:15,209 --> 01:09:17,918
<font color="#ffff80">It's absurd to poison
someone with TH-16,</font>

799
01:09:18,084 --> 01:09:19,834
<font color="#ffff80">then steal the body.</font>

800
01:09:20,001 --> 01:09:22,293
<font color="#ffff80">It's undetectable in
a routine autopsy.</font>

801
01:09:22,459 --> 01:09:25,501
<font color="#ffff80">It wasn't your specialty
before, now you're an expert.</font>

802
01:09:25,668 --> 01:09:27,293
<font color="#ffff80">I was nervous before.</font>

803
01:09:27,459 --> 01:09:31,001
<font color="#ffff80">If you want a confession to
close the case, forget it.</font>

804
01:09:31,168 --> 01:09:33,251
<font color="#ffff80">You've got nothing on me.</font>

805
01:09:33,668 --> 01:09:36,959
<font color="#ffff80">I just need to show that something
went wrong so you took the body!</font>

806
01:09:37,126 --> 01:09:40,793
<font color="#ffff80">You need to find Mayka, and
I can't help you with that.</font>

807
01:09:40,959 --> 01:09:42,668
<font color="#ffff80">I've no idea where she is.</font>

808
01:09:49,668 --> 01:09:51,251
<font color="#ffff80">How did you meet your wife?</font>

809
01:09:51,876 --> 01:09:55,501
<font color="#ffff80">- What does that matter?
- Curiosity. Too many differences.</font>

810
01:09:55,793 --> 01:09:57,793
<font color="#ffff80">- Differences?
- In age,...</font>

811
01:09:58,043 --> 01:10:00,584
<font color="#ffff80">...status, everything.</font>

812
01:10:03,709 --> 01:10:04,959
<font color="#ffff80">Answer me.</font>

813
01:10:06,501 --> 01:10:09,418
<font color="#ffff80">It was in Avalon,</font>

814
01:10:09,584 --> 01:10:11,876
<font color="#ffff80">on Santa Catalina
Island, near L.A.</font>

815
01:10:12,293 --> 01:10:15,251
<font color="#ffff80">I spent some days there after my
first year in the university.</font>

816
01:10:15,418 --> 01:10:16,834
<font color="#ffff80">You taught Chemistry.</font>

817
01:10:17,001 --> 01:10:20,293
<font color="#ffff80">Yes. I didn't like it. I took
a trip to think it over.</font>

818
01:10:20,709 --> 01:10:24,959
<font color="#ffff80">One morning, going up a
mountain, a tyre blew out.</font>

819
01:10:25,209 --> 01:10:27,834
<font color="#ffff80">Mayka was the only person
I saw in three hours.</font>

820
01:10:28,001 --> 01:10:30,126
<font color="#ffff80">She gave me water, her mobile...</font>

821
01:10:30,293 --> 01:10:32,126
<font color="#ffff80">and I changed the tyre.</font>

822
01:10:32,293 --> 01:10:35,543
<font color="#ffff80">- Lost on an island...
- We were at the same hotel.</font>

823
01:10:36,251 --> 01:10:38,876
<font color="#ffff80">She'd just lost her parents
and felt lost, like I did.</font>

824
01:10:39,043 --> 01:10:42,626
<font color="#ffff80">Lost but a millionaire. She'd
just inherited a fortune.</font>

825
01:10:43,793 --> 01:10:47,251
<font color="#ffff80">- We fell in love.
- How nice, like in the movies.</font>

826
01:10:47,418 --> 01:10:50,668
<font color="#ffff80">It's what happened. I was lucky.</font>

827
01:10:52,126 --> 01:10:53,876
<font color="#ffff80">Luck's something you have...</font>

828
01:10:54,418 --> 01:10:56,043
<font color="#ffff80">or you seek it out.</font>

829
01:10:56,209 --> 01:10:57,834
<font color="#ffff80">What do you think?</font>

830
01:10:59,876 --> 01:11:01,918
<font color="#ffff80">What the hell do
you want from me?</font>

831
01:11:11,209 --> 01:11:14,459
<font color="#ffff80">Let's go back to when you
found your wife's body.</font>

832
01:11:14,626 --> 01:11:17,209
<font color="#ffff80">I told the police who
came to my house.</font>

833
01:11:17,376 --> 01:11:19,168
<font color="#ffff80">I want you to tell me.</font>

834
01:11:23,334 --> 01:11:27,751
<font color="#ffff80">I came home and Mayka was
lying on the sofa, dead.</font>

835
01:11:28,584 --> 01:11:30,751
<font color="#ffff80">I thought she was asleep,</font>

836
01:11:31,043 --> 01:11:33,834
<font color="#ffff80">but it was strange that
she had her shoes on.</font>

837
01:11:34,001 --> 01:11:37,626
<font color="#ffff80">I took her pulse, called an ambulance,
and they called the police.</font>

838
01:11:37,793 --> 01:11:40,418
<font color="#ffff80">- And the last time you saw her alive?
- That morning.</font>

839
01:11:40,584 --> 01:11:44,001
<font color="#ffff80">Three weeks apart. She
arrives and you leave.</font>

840
01:11:44,168 --> 01:11:47,043
<font color="#ffff80">What are you insinuating?
I loved my wife.</font>

841
01:11:47,209 --> 01:11:50,793
<font color="#ffff80">- You loved her?
- I loved her to the last moment.</font>

842
01:11:52,293 --> 01:11:55,543
<font color="#ffff80">Don't you still love someone
after they're dead?</font>

843
01:12:01,126 --> 01:12:05,126
<font color="#ffff80">Your calm at her unexpected death
surprises me, it's unnerving.</font>

844
01:12:06,543 --> 01:12:10,084
<font color="#ffff80">I'm a scientist, I know
we're not machines.</font>

845
01:12:10,376 --> 01:12:12,959
<font color="#ffff80">I heard the forensic person:
a fear of flying can...</font>

846
01:12:13,126 --> 01:12:16,209
<font color="#ffff80">A handy theory for you, eh?
I'm sure you already knew.</font>

847
01:12:16,709 --> 01:12:20,709
<font color="#ffff80">I had a heart scare two years
ago, with no previous signs.</font>

848
01:12:21,959 --> 01:12:24,376
<font color="#ffff80">These things come
without warning.</font>

849
01:12:24,543 --> 01:12:27,793
<font color="#ffff80">What did you do after your
wife's body was taken away?</font>

850
01:12:30,459 --> 01:12:32,543
<font color="#ffff80">I made some calls, I cried...</font>

851
01:12:33,043 --> 01:12:36,001
<font color="#ffff80">Gloria, Luna and my sister came
over, we reminisced about Mayka.</font>

852
01:12:36,293 --> 01:12:37,626
<font color="#ffff80">And later?</font>

853
01:12:37,793 --> 01:12:41,293
<font color="#ffff80">Gloria, Luna and your
sister went home.</font>

854
01:12:41,626 --> 01:12:44,543
<font color="#ffff80">- What did you do then?
- Nothing.</font>

855
01:12:44,709 --> 01:12:46,876
<font color="#ffff80">We sent a patrol car for you.
You weren't at home.</font>

856
01:12:47,501 --> 01:12:49,584
<font color="#ffff80">I went out for painkillers.
I told you.</font>

857
01:12:49,751 --> 01:12:52,043
<font color="#ffff80">- Painkillers...
- Yes. I had a headache.</font>

858
01:12:52,709 --> 01:12:55,459
<font color="#ffff80">You came straight
here after our call.</font>

859
01:12:55,959 --> 01:12:57,251
<font color="#ffff80">Exactly.</font>

860
01:12:57,418 --> 01:13:00,584
<font color="#ffff80">So you have the painkillers.
Show them to me.</font>

861
01:13:06,793 --> 01:13:07,876
<font color="#ffff80">This is absurd.</font>

862
01:13:08,043 --> 01:13:09,501
<font color="#ffff80">Convince me.</font>

863
01:13:14,709 --> 01:13:16,626
<font color="#ffff80">Now you're ringing true.</font>

864
01:13:17,293 --> 01:13:20,793
<font color="#ffff80">And as a reward, I'll give
you proof of my theory.</font>

865
01:13:23,918 --> 01:13:25,793
<font color="#ffff80">Proof you say I don't have.</font>

866
01:13:31,459 --> 01:13:34,709
<font color="#ffff80">Your wife hired a detective
three months ago.</font>

867
01:13:35,251 --> 01:13:37,501
<font color="#ffff80">He's been following
you, Mr. Ulloa.</font>

868
01:13:38,334 --> 01:13:40,084
<font color="#ffff80">We have the invoice.</font>

869
01:13:40,668 --> 01:13:44,168
<font color="#ffff80">And also your marriage contract.</font>

870
01:13:47,376 --> 01:13:50,459
<font color="#ffff80">I think your wife suspected
you of cheating on her.</font>

871
01:13:51,043 --> 01:13:52,043
<font color="#ffff80">If so,</font>

872
01:13:52,209 --> 01:13:56,459
<font color="#ffff80">you would've violated one
of the main clauses,</font>

873
01:13:56,959 --> 01:14:01,459
<font color="#ffff80">and you'd lose all rights
if your wife divorced you.</font>

874
01:14:01,959 --> 01:14:05,126
<font color="#ffff80">The question is: Did the
detective catch you?</font>

875
01:14:07,668 --> 01:14:10,293
<font color="#ffff80">I think you know the
answer to that,</font>

876
01:14:10,959 --> 01:14:14,126
<font color="#ffff80">and you killed her before she
cut you off with nothing.</font>

877
01:14:14,418 --> 01:14:16,251
<font color="#ffff80">We'll soon know for sure.</font>

878
01:14:16,501 --> 01:14:19,793
<font color="#ffff80">A patrol car is heading for
the home of Javier Alonso.</font>

879
01:14:23,584 --> 01:14:25,001
<font color="#ffff80">Javier Alonso?</font>

880
01:14:25,376 --> 01:14:27,251
<font color="#ffff80">Your wife's detective.</font>

881
01:14:32,918 --> 01:14:35,501
<font color="#ffff80">Anything true you'd like to add?</font>

882
01:14:44,709 --> 01:14:46,043
<font color="#ffff80">Look at the name.</font>

883
01:14:52,459 --> 01:14:53,751
<font color="#ffff80">Diego Aguilar.</font>

884
01:15:00,918 --> 01:15:02,168
<font color="#ffff80">What are you doing?</font>

885
01:15:32,918 --> 01:15:34,001
<font color="#ffff80">Go ahead, Pablo.</font>

886
01:15:34,168 --> 01:15:37,043
<font color="#ffff80">We're in Alonso's office and
there's no trace of him</font>

887
01:15:37,209 --> 01:15:40,168
<font color="#ffff80">or any of the cases
he was investigating.</font>

888
01:15:40,334 --> 01:15:42,668
<font color="#ffff80">Someone's taken his hard disk.</font>

889
01:15:42,918 --> 01:15:44,959
<font color="#ffff80">Register of last calls?
Messages?</font>

890
01:15:45,126 --> 01:15:46,584
<font color="#ffff80">There's nothing here, Jaime.</font>

891
01:15:46,751 --> 01:15:47,918
<font color="#ffff80">Go to Ulloa's house.</font>

892
01:15:48,251 --> 01:15:52,001
<font color="#ffff80">- I'll call the judge for a warrant.
- Okay.</font>

893
01:15:52,459 --> 01:15:54,168
<font color="#ffff80">Where's the transfer car?</font>

894
01:15:57,043 --> 01:15:58,626
<font color="#ffff80">Norma here. Do you read me?</font>

895
01:15:59,251 --> 01:16:00,418
<font color="#ffff80">I read you. Go ahead.</font>

896
01:16:00,584 --> 01:16:03,168
<font color="#ffff80">Central said you were coming.
What's the delay?</font>

897
01:16:03,334 --> 01:16:06,043
<font color="#ffff80">The road's cut off.</font>

898
01:16:06,209 --> 01:16:09,084
<font color="#ffff80">The storm tore down
some power lines.</font>

899
01:16:09,293 --> 01:16:12,293
<font color="#ffff80">They don't know how long
it'll take to shift them.</font>

900
01:16:27,543 --> 01:16:28,876
<font color="#ffff80">Any news?</font>

901
01:16:29,043 --> 01:16:33,126
<font color="#ffff80">Yeah, babe. I'm knackered.
Want me to get you a coffee?</font>

902
01:17:13,293 --> 01:17:15,626
<font color="#ffff80">- Alex, is that you?
- Javier Alonso is a detective</font>

903
01:17:16,293 --> 01:17:17,501
<font color="#ffff80">I know.</font>

904
01:17:17,834 --> 01:17:20,293
<font color="#ffff80">- You found him?
- Not exactly.</font>

905
01:17:20,459 --> 01:17:24,126
<font color="#ffff80">Someone put an envelope under my
door while I was at the hospital.</font>

906
01:17:27,126 --> 01:17:29,168
<font color="#ffff80">There was a pendrive in it.</font>

907
01:17:29,334 --> 01:17:32,126
<font color="#ffff80">- Is it from Javier Alonso?
- No sender.</font>

908
01:17:32,293 --> 01:17:36,376
<font color="#ffff80">It has a file in his name.
I'm sending you the photos.</font>

909
01:17:46,168 --> 01:17:47,334
<font color="#ffff80">Alex?</font>

910
01:17:50,251 --> 01:17:50,876
<font color="#ffff80">Alex!</font>

911
01:17:51,543 --> 01:17:52,626
<font color="#ffff80">Yes...</font>

912
01:17:52,918 --> 01:17:56,709
<font color="#ffff80">That's not all. They put
a mike on you. Listen.</font>

913
01:17:56,876 --> 01:17:58,709
<font color="#ffff80">I've got everything.</font>

914
01:17:58,876 --> 01:18:01,501
<font color="#ffff80">Mayka's going to L.A. soon.
It'll be when she comes back.</font>

915
01:18:01,668 --> 01:18:04,543
<font color="#ffff80">She hates flying. It'll
explain the heart attack.</font>

916
01:18:06,918 --> 01:18:08,668
<font color="#ffff80">Mayka knew everything.</font>

917
01:18:09,501 --> 01:18:11,501
<font color="#ffff80">She sent it. She'll
be coming for you.</font>

918
01:18:12,168 --> 01:18:14,251
<font color="#ffff80">- You have to leave! Now!
- I am.</font>

919
01:18:14,418 --> 01:18:15,584
<font color="#ffff80">We'll be together soon.</font>

920
01:18:15,751 --> 01:18:18,001
<font color="#ffff80">You've been saying that all
night and you're still there.</font>

921
01:18:18,293 --> 01:18:20,751
<font color="#ffff80">The main thing now
is to get you safe.</font>

922
01:18:20,918 --> 01:18:23,459
<font color="#ffff80">- And you?
- I'm fine.</font>

923
01:18:23,959 --> 01:18:26,459
<font color="#ffff80">How can you be fine? Alex,
they won't let you go!</font>

924
01:18:27,001 --> 01:18:28,834
<font color="#ffff80">Of course they will.</font>

925
01:18:29,001 --> 01:18:32,168
<font color="#ffff80">- They'll make you confess!
- Listen to me, listen.</font>

926
01:18:33,251 --> 01:18:36,043
<font color="#ffff80">If Mayka's still alive, they
can't accuse us of anything.</font>

927
01:18:36,209 --> 01:18:38,543
<font color="#ffff80">She knows it and wants us
to pay in her own way.</font>

928
01:18:38,709 --> 01:18:40,209
<font color="#ffff80">She can do what she wants.</font>

929
01:18:40,376 --> 01:18:42,709
<font color="#ffff80">She's certified as dead,
she's free of any blame.</font>

930
01:18:42,876 --> 01:18:45,251
<font color="#ffff80">But I promise, nothing bad
will happen to you, okay?</font>

931
01:18:45,418 --> 01:18:47,126
<font color="#ffff80">I can't take this any more.</font>

932
01:18:47,959 --> 01:18:50,334
<font color="#ffff80">You and I should never have met.</font>

933
01:18:51,501 --> 01:18:52,834
<font color="#ffff80">Carla, I love you.</font>

934
01:18:53,001 --> 01:18:55,918
<font color="#ffff80">- And I love you, but...
- Then trust me, please.</font>

935
01:18:58,834 --> 01:19:00,209
<font color="#ffff80">What was that?</font>

936
01:19:01,001 --> 01:19:02,959
<font color="#ffff80">The lift is stuck.</font>

937
01:19:03,293 --> 01:19:04,626
<font color="#ffff80">Are you trapped?</font>

938
01:19:04,959 --> 01:19:06,918
<font color="#ffff80">Fuck. It's stuck!</font>

939
01:19:07,084 --> 01:19:08,543
<font color="#ffff80">Push the alarm.</font>

940
01:19:09,501 --> 01:19:10,709
<font color="#ffff80">What's happening now?</font>

941
01:19:11,584 --> 01:19:13,126
<font color="#ffff80">It's moving.</font>

942
01:19:14,001 --> 01:19:15,459
<font color="#ffff80">But are you alright?</font>

943
01:19:16,626 --> 01:19:17,793
<font color="#ffff80">I don't know.</font>

944
01:19:18,709 --> 01:19:23,043
<font color="#ffff80">I get the feeling someone's
here, that I'm not alone.</font>

945
01:19:27,834 --> 01:19:28,959
<font color="#ffff80">Carla, are you alright?</font>

946
01:19:30,126 --> 01:19:32,626
<font color="#ffff80">Do anything to get out
of there and join me.</font>

947
01:19:32,793 --> 01:19:34,126
<font color="#ffff80">I promise.</font>

948
01:19:34,293 --> 01:19:36,543
<font color="#ffff80">We'll soon be together.
It'll all be fine.</font>

949
01:19:36,709 --> 01:19:39,626
<font color="#ffff80">Don't abandon me.
- Don '1' worry. Where will I find you?</font>

950
01:19:39,793 --> 01:19:43,418
<font color="#ffff80">- In the car.
- Good, go for a drive.</font>

951
01:19:43,584 --> 01:19:45,793
<font color="#ffff80">Don't stop, that'll be safest.</font>

952
01:19:47,709 --> 01:19:48,793
<font color="#ffff80">Carla?</font>

953
01:19:52,459 --> 01:19:53,626
<font color="#ffff80">Carla?</font>

954
01:19:55,418 --> 01:19:56,834
<font color="#ffff80">Carla!</font>

955
01:20:06,168 --> 01:20:07,418
<font color="#ffff80">What's he doing?</font>

956
01:20:19,418 --> 01:20:21,251
<font color="#ffff80">- Where the hell are you going?
- I've got to go.</font>

957
01:20:21,418 --> 01:20:23,543
<font color="#ffff80">I give the orders here and
you're in my custody.</font>

958
01:20:23,709 --> 01:20:25,209
<font color="#ffff80">Someone needs my help.</font>

959
01:20:25,376 --> 01:20:26,668
<font color="#ffff80">- Your help?
- Yes.</font>

960
01:20:26,834 --> 01:20:28,043
<font color="#ffff80">Who?</font>

961
01:20:28,543 --> 01:20:32,084
<font color="#ffff80">Who the hell do you think you are?
You think you can hold me?</font>

962
01:20:32,251 --> 01:20:35,168
<font color="#ffff80">You've got no fucking idea
of what I'm capable of!</font>

963
01:20:36,084 --> 01:20:37,751
<font color="#ffff80">Piss off!</font>

964
01:20:46,668 --> 01:20:47,918
<font color="#ffff80">Alright.</font>

965
01:20:49,251 --> 01:20:51,084
<font color="#ffff80">Yes, that's the address.</font>

966
01:20:55,293 --> 01:20:56,959
<font color="#ffff80">Call me if there's any news.</font>

967
01:20:59,668 --> 01:21:03,543
<font color="#ffff80">A patrol car is heading for
the address you gave us.</font>

968
01:21:03,709 --> 01:21:06,959
<font color="#ffff80">Now tell me everything again,</font>

969
01:21:07,834 --> 01:21:09,334
<font color="#ffff80">from the beginning.</font>

970
01:21:21,293 --> 01:21:24,001
<font color="#ffff80">Her name's Carla, Carla Miller.</font>

971
01:21:24,584 --> 01:21:25,834
<font color="#ffff80">I met her 8 months ago.</font>

972
01:21:26,001 --> 01:21:27,959
<font color="#ffff80">Class B, transposition...</font>

973
01:21:28,126 --> 01:21:30,501
<font color="#ffff80">I was giving a talk
at the university.</font>

974
01:21:30,668 --> 01:21:33,584
<font color="#ffff80">I'd been arguing with Mayka
and I couldn't concentrate.</font>

975
01:21:33,751 --> 01:21:37,293
<font color="#ffff80">I kept losing the thread. I
was about to stop the class</font>

976
01:21:37,501 --> 01:21:40,834
<font color="#ffff80">when she arrived,
twenty minutes late</font>

977
01:21:41,793 --> 01:21:43,126
<font color="#ffff80">Excuse me.</font>

978
01:21:44,251 --> 01:21:45,501
<font color="#ffff80">Come in, come in.</font>

979
01:21:51,668 --> 01:21:53,168
<font color="#ffff80">In this process,</font>

980
01:21:54,418 --> 01:21:56,293
<font color="#ffff80">the proteins</font>

981
01:21:56,459 --> 01:21:59,251
<font color="#ffff80">can behave as co-factors...</font>

982
01:22:00,459 --> 01:22:02,543
<font color="#ffff80">...in an approximate
percentage...</font>

983
01:22:02,709 --> 01:22:05,084
<font color="#ffff80">She came up and asked me
if she'd missed anything.</font>

984
01:22:05,251 --> 01:22:07,251
<font color="#ffff80">I said yes. I lied to her.</font>

985
01:22:08,501 --> 01:22:10,959
<font color="#ffff80">She snared me straightaway.</font>

986
01:22:12,709 --> 01:22:17,084
<font color="#ffff80">She'd started Medicine. She was
struggling with Chemistry.</font>

987
01:22:17,251 --> 01:22:19,126
<font color="#ffff80">I offered to help her.</font>

988
01:22:19,668 --> 01:22:22,543
<font color="#ffff80">It was all very easy. It
seemed natural to me.</font>

989
01:22:22,709 --> 01:22:26,376
<font color="#ffff80">At first we worked, but the
classes became an excuse</font>

990
01:22:26,543 --> 01:22:29,126
<font color="#ffff80">and we began seeing
each other every day.</font>

991
01:22:30,584 --> 01:22:34,084
<font color="#ffff80">I wanted to be honest, and
told her I was married</font>

992
01:22:34,251 --> 01:22:37,168
<font color="#ffff80">She had a boyfriend,
so it was all fine.</font>

993
01:22:39,543 --> 01:22:40,709
<font color="#ffff80">What are you doing here?</font>

994
01:22:40,876 --> 01:22:44,293
<font color="#ffff80">It was a harmless game. We
didn't do anything, just talked.</font>

995
01:22:45,293 --> 01:22:47,543
<font color="#ffff80">But we spent so
much time together</font>

996
01:22:48,334 --> 01:22:49,626
<font color="#ffff80">that Mayka began to suspect.</font>

997
01:22:49,793 --> 01:22:51,501
<font color="#ffff80">I expected you earlier.</font>

998
01:22:52,126 --> 01:22:53,793
<font color="#ffff80">I tried to stop seeing her.</font>

999
01:22:53,959 --> 01:22:57,209
<font color="#ffff80">But it was impossible, all
I could think of was her.</font>

1000
01:22:57,459 --> 01:23:00,959
<font color="#ffff80">In the end, the
inevitable happened.</font>

1001
01:23:51,293 --> 01:23:53,543
<font color="#ffff80">With Carla I felt alive again.</font>

1002
01:23:54,626 --> 01:23:58,043
<font color="#ffff80">That night, I told
her my life story,</font>

1003
01:23:58,668 --> 01:24:00,751
<font color="#ffff80">things I'd never told anyone.</font>

1004
01:24:00,918 --> 01:24:02,918
<font color="#ffff80">Neither of us wanted secrets.</font>

1005
01:24:04,376 --> 01:24:05,793
<font color="#ffff80">But there was my wife...</font>

1006
01:24:07,043 --> 01:24:09,084
<font color="#ffff80">She said she didn't
want to deceive anyone.</font>

1007
01:24:09,251 --> 01:24:12,834
<font color="#ffff80">I didn't want to deceive my wife,
but I was in love with Carla.</font>

1008
01:24:13,001 --> 01:24:15,001
<font color="#ffff80">She left her boyfriend for me.</font>

1009
01:24:16,001 --> 01:24:19,543
<font color="#ffff80">But I wasn't ready to
tell Mayka the truth.</font>

1010
01:24:19,751 --> 01:24:21,501
<font color="#ffff80">And Carla got tired of waiting.</font>

1011
01:24:21,668 --> 01:24:23,418
<font color="#ffff80">She refused to see me any more.</font>

1012
01:24:23,793 --> 01:24:25,584
<font color="#ffff80">And she vanished from the map.</font>

1013
01:24:26,043 --> 01:24:27,459
<font color="#ffff80">I went crazy.</font>

1014
01:24:27,709 --> 01:24:30,043
<font color="#ffff80">I couldn't live without her.
I had to do something.</font>

1015
01:24:30,668 --> 01:24:33,084
<font color="#ffff80">There was no going back.
I was in love.</font>

1016
01:24:33,251 --> 01:24:35,251
<font color="#ffff80">And I decided. I
went to see her.</font>

1017
01:24:36,376 --> 01:24:40,459
<font color="#ffff80">I told her it was over with Mayka,
I'd leave her to be with her.</font>

1018
01:24:41,751 --> 01:24:43,751
<font color="#ffff80">I love you.</font>

1019
01:24:45,834 --> 01:24:47,501
<font color="#ffff80">But it wasn't that easy.</font>

1020
01:24:48,043 --> 01:24:50,418
<font color="#ffff80">Mayka was stalking
me, watching me.</font>

1021
01:24:50,584 --> 01:24:53,918
<font color="#ffff80">I knew a divorce would
mean war, and she'd win.</font>

1022
01:24:54,751 --> 01:24:56,668
<font color="#ffff80">She'd destroy me. She'd
leave me with nothing.</font>

1023
01:24:56,834 --> 01:24:59,501
<font color="#ffff80">She'd make me start from nothing
to show she was still in control.</font>

1024
01:24:59,668 --> 01:25:02,126
<font color="#ffff80">You say you want to be with me,
but you don't want a divorce.</font>

1025
01:25:02,293 --> 01:25:04,918
<font color="#ffff80">I don't want to be with you
while you're with her.</font>

1026
01:25:05,084 --> 01:25:06,584
<font color="#ffff80">I can't take any more.</font>

1027
01:25:07,043 --> 01:25:10,459
<font color="#ffff80">This is over, I can't
take any more.</font>

1028
01:25:23,334 --> 01:25:26,584
<font color="#ffff80">I can stop being with her
without getting a divorce.</font>

1029
01:25:27,209 --> 01:25:28,918
<font color="#ffff80">We can have it all.</font>

1030
01:25:30,043 --> 01:25:32,334
<font color="#ffff80">She could have an accident.</font>

1031
01:25:33,418 --> 01:25:35,751
<font color="#ffff80">I need to know if
Carla's alright.</font>

1032
01:25:36,876 --> 01:25:38,668
<font color="#ffff80">There's something I don't get.</font>

1033
01:25:40,209 --> 01:25:43,543
<font color="#ffff80">If you carefully planned
your wife's death,</font>

1034
01:25:43,793 --> 01:25:46,668
<font color="#ffff80">sure of the toxin's
infallibility,</font>

1035
01:25:47,001 --> 01:25:48,543
<font color="#ffff80">why would she be alive?</font>

1036
01:25:50,418 --> 01:25:51,251
<font color="#ffff80">I saw you.</font>

1037
01:25:51,418 --> 01:25:53,543
<font color="#ffff80">Your wife hired a detective
three months ago.</font>

1038
01:25:53,709 --> 01:25:55,293
<font color="#ffff80">There are a lot of things
you don't know about me.</font>

1039
01:25:55,459 --> 01:25:56,959
<font color="#ffff80">Mayka's going to L.A. soon.</font>

1040
01:25:57,126 --> 01:25:59,459
<font color="#ffff80">Her fear of flying can
explain a heart attack.</font>

1041
01:25:59,626 --> 01:26:02,709
<font color="#ffff80">Someone put an envelope under my
door while I was at the hospital.</font>

1042
01:26:02,876 --> 01:26:04,043
<font color="#ffff80">Mayka knew everything.</font>

1043
01:26:04,334 --> 01:26:08,084
<font color="#ffff80">How did she avoid dying? You
saw her drink the wine.</font>

1044
01:26:11,668 --> 01:26:13,376
<font color="#ffff80">She could've switched glasses.</font>

1045
01:26:19,251 --> 01:26:22,918
<font color="#ffff80">If she did, what do you
think happened next?</font>

1046
01:26:23,084 --> 01:26:27,334
<font color="#ffff80">She could've taken a neuroleptic
to enter a state of catalepsy.</font>

1047
01:26:28,043 --> 01:26:31,001
<font color="#ffff80">Some can be diluted
in the blood,</font>

1048
01:26:31,168 --> 01:26:33,709
<font color="#ffff80">slow down the lungs and
virtually stop the heart.</font>

1049
01:26:35,126 --> 01:26:38,084
<font color="#ffff80">Once the agent metabolizes
in the organism,</font>

1050
01:26:38,584 --> 01:26:40,334
<font color="#ffff80">the body returns to normal.</font>

1051
01:26:40,501 --> 01:26:42,959
<font color="#ffff80">A little twisted. And dangerous.</font>

1052
01:26:43,126 --> 01:26:44,876
<font color="#ffff80">Not for Mayka.</font>

1053
01:26:47,168 --> 01:26:48,751
<font color="#ffff80">She likes to play.</font>

1054
01:26:49,751 --> 01:26:51,793
<font color="#ffff80">And she hates to lose.</font>

1055
01:26:53,334 --> 01:26:56,001
<font color="#ffff80">Listen, I've told
you everything.</font>

1056
01:26:56,584 --> 01:26:59,501
<font color="#ffff80">Please, ask after Carla.</font>

1057
01:27:03,084 --> 01:27:03,918
<font color="#ffff80">Jaime.</font>

1058
01:27:07,168 --> 01:27:08,626
<font color="#ffff80">I'll be right back.</font>

1059
01:27:09,043 --> 01:27:11,751
<font color="#ffff80">- Who is it?
- Pablo, from Ulloa's house.</font>

1060
01:27:14,584 --> 01:27:15,376
<font color="#ffff80">Go ahead.</font>

1061
01:27:15,543 --> 01:27:18,376
<font color="#ffff80">We found plans of the morgue.
There's a route mapped out</font>

1062
01:27:18,543 --> 01:27:22,126
<font color="#ffff80">and instructions on how to
manipulate the security system.</font>

1063
01:27:22,459 --> 01:27:24,293
<font color="#ffff80">We're taking all the papers.</font>

1064
01:27:24,459 --> 01:27:27,001
<font color="#ffff80">- He knew the building backwards.
- Any trace of the body?</font>

1065
01:27:27,168 --> 01:27:28,084
<font color="#ffff80">No, but we found</font>

1066
01:27:28,251 --> 01:27:30,834
<font color="#ffff80">a shovel and a sports bag
in the boot of Ulla's car.</font>

1067
01:27:31,001 --> 01:27:33,168
<font color="#ffff80">In it were a balaclava
and some trainers</font>

1068
01:27:33,334 --> 01:27:37,168
<font color="#ffff80">that match the footprints on the
morgue 's emergency stairs.</font>

1069
01:27:37,584 --> 01:27:38,418
<font color="#ffff80">Anything else?</font>

1070
01:27:38,584 --> 01:27:42,293
<font color="#ffff80">We also found a '32
hidden in a box.</font>

1071
01:27:42,459 --> 01:27:46,168
<font color="#ffff80">It's unregistered and has
been fired recently.</font>

1072
01:27:46,793 --> 01:27:48,418
<font color="#ffff80">What the hell's going on?</font>

1073
01:27:49,709 --> 01:27:50,959
<font color="#ffff80">I've got another call.</font>

1074
01:27:53,418 --> 01:27:54,251
<font color="#ffff80">What is it?</font>

1075
01:27:54,501 --> 01:27:56,376
<font color="#ffff80">Angel Torres is awake.</font>

1076
01:27:56,626 --> 01:27:58,459
<font color="#ffff80">- Hold on.
- Okay.</font>

1077
01:28:01,668 --> 01:28:03,418
<font color="#ffff80">The guard is conscious.</font>

1078
01:28:04,084 --> 01:28:07,334
<font color="#ffff80">I'll pass you to the hospital.
We're heading for the woods.</font>

1079
01:28:08,168 --> 01:28:09,459
<font color="#ffff80">- Jaime.
- How is he?</font>

1080
01:28:09,626 --> 01:28:12,043
<font color="#ffff80">Disoriented, but I spoke to him.</font>

1081
01:28:12,209 --> 01:28:14,834
<font color="#ffff80">- What did he say?
- You're not gonna believe it.</font>

1082
01:28:15,001 --> 01:28:16,084
<font color="#ffff80">Fire away.</font>

1083
01:29:55,668 --> 01:29:57,084
<font color="#ffff80">Hello?</font>

1084
01:30:13,168 --> 01:30:16,876
<font color="#ffff80">Yes. This is Angel Torres.
I'm calling from the morgue.</font>

1085
01:30:17,043 --> 01:30:19,918
<font color="#ffff80">I think... I need
you to come here.</font>

1086
01:30:20,293 --> 01:30:23,459
<font color="#ffff80">Yes, I'll wait. Hurry up.</font>

1087
01:30:46,168 --> 01:30:48,959
<font color="#ffff80">He ran out of the morgue
like a scared rat</font>

1088
01:30:49,126 --> 01:30:50,751
<font color="#ffff80">until he was run over.</font>

1089
01:30:51,793 --> 01:30:54,543
<font color="#ffff80">We just found them.
They're from a '32,</font>

1090
01:30:55,293 --> 01:30:56,626
<font color="#ffff80">like the gun at your house.</font>

1091
01:30:56,959 --> 01:30:59,293
<font color="#ffff80">I don't own a gun. It was Mayka.</font>

1092
01:30:59,584 --> 01:31:01,584
<font color="#ffff80">Your wife's dead, Mr. Ulloa.
Dead.</font>

1093
01:31:01,751 --> 01:31:05,084
<font color="#ffff80">You can't prove it. They haven't
found the body, nor will they.</font>

1094
01:31:05,251 --> 01:31:07,626
<font color="#ffff80">- Because you took it!
- I didn't do anything.</font>

1095
01:31:07,793 --> 01:31:10,418
<font color="#ffff80">You motherfucker! You killed
her, then took her away.</font>

1096
01:31:10,584 --> 01:31:12,793
<font color="#ffff80">Mayka wants you to think that.
Can't you see?</font>

1097
01:31:13,876 --> 01:31:16,584
<font color="#ffff80">Mayka's behind it all. She set
it up with someone's help.</font>

1098
01:31:16,751 --> 01:31:19,626
<font color="#ffff80">She faked her disappearance
and made sure she'd wake up.</font>

1099
01:31:27,418 --> 01:31:29,501
<font color="#ffff80">She's fucking alive!
She's alive!</font>

1100
01:31:29,668 --> 01:31:31,668
<font color="#ffff80">No! You took her body!</font>

1101
01:31:31,834 --> 01:31:34,251
<font color="#ffff80">The plans to the morgue
were hidden in your house.</font>

1102
01:31:34,418 --> 01:31:35,668
<font color="#ffff80">You had it all worked out.</font>

1103
01:31:35,834 --> 01:31:38,251
<font color="#ffff80">You distracted the
guard to confuse us.</font>

1104
01:31:38,418 --> 01:31:42,376
<font color="#ffff80">You knew he'd confuse us,
but then he got run over,</font>

1105
01:31:42,543 --> 01:31:45,709
<font color="#ffff80">so you've been winging it
all night, playing with us!</font>

1106
01:31:45,876 --> 01:31:47,751
<font color="#ffff80">What does it matter now?</font>

1107
01:31:49,668 --> 01:31:52,751
<font color="#ffff80">It was set up so that Mayka
would be declared dead,</font>

1108
01:31:52,918 --> 01:31:54,043
<font color="#ffff80">and I'd confess.</font>

1109
01:31:58,709 --> 01:32:02,543
<font color="#ffff80">Nothing that happened
tonight was an accident,</font>

1110
01:32:02,709 --> 01:32:04,126
<font color="#ffff80">believe me.</font>

1111
01:32:04,543 --> 01:32:08,793
<font color="#ffff80">Mayka has the power and money
to vanish without a trace.</font>

1112
01:32:09,668 --> 01:32:13,418
<font color="#ffff80">It's perfect. She
left no loose ends.</font>

1113
01:32:16,001 --> 01:32:19,876
<font color="#ffff80">If it's not too late, Carla
will corroborate my story.</font>

1114
01:32:20,043 --> 01:32:23,334
<font color="#ffff80">How do you keep justifying
the unjustifiable?</font>

1115
01:32:23,584 --> 01:32:26,418
<font color="#ffff80">Don't you get tired?
Aren't you disgusted?</font>

1116
01:32:27,959 --> 01:32:29,334
<font color="#ffff80">Please...</font>

1117
01:32:30,793 --> 01:32:32,709
<font color="#ffff80">I need you to help Carla.</font>

1118
01:32:34,084 --> 01:32:35,376
<font color="#ffff80">Please.</font>

1119
01:33:21,626 --> 01:33:23,209
<font color="#ffff80">Any news on Carla Miller?</font>

1120
01:33:23,376 --> 01:33:24,376
<font color="#ffff80">There's no one here.</font>

1121
01:33:24,543 --> 01:33:26,001
<font color="#ffff80">- An y signs of violence?
- No.</font>

1122
01:33:26,168 --> 01:33:28,626
<font color="#ffff80">The suspect claims
the girl was warned.</font>

1123
01:33:28,793 --> 01:33:30,543
<font color="#ffff80">Could she have run away?</font>

1124
01:33:30,709 --> 01:33:34,668
<font color="#ffff80">If she hasn't, someone's
made it look that way.</font>

1125
01:33:36,668 --> 01:33:38,709
<font color="#ffff80">I'll call you if
there's any news.</font>

1126
01:33:44,584 --> 01:33:46,418
<font color="#ffff80">Tow truck to the coordinates.
Copy that.</font>

1127
01:33:46,584 --> 01:33:48,543
<font color="#ffff80">I don't know what
we'll find there.</font>

1128
01:33:48,709 --> 01:33:50,751
<font color="#ffff80">I'll await instructions
and tell HQ.</font>

1129
01:33:50,918 --> 01:33:53,626
<font color="#ffff80">The tow truck will be 15 minutes.
Everything else in order?</font>

1130
01:33:53,793 --> 01:33:56,959
<font color="#ffff80">- Yes, but I need the traffic diverted.
- I'll tell them.</font>

1131
01:33:59,584 --> 01:34:02,626
<font color="#ffff80">Jaime's here now. When I speak
to him, I'll relay the info.</font>

1132
01:34:04,376 --> 01:34:06,293
<font color="#ffff80">We've found a body.</font>

1133
01:34:07,209 --> 01:34:08,626
<font color="#ffff80">Tell Norma and Mateos.</font>

1134
01:35:38,834 --> 01:35:42,584
<font color="#ffff80">No one lives at the address
you gave us for Carla Miller.</font>

1135
01:35:43,543 --> 01:35:45,876
<font color="#ffff80">The flat's been
vacant for years.</font>

1136
01:35:47,209 --> 01:35:50,293
<font color="#ffff80">And the neighbours can't
recall any Carla Miller.</font>

1137
01:35:51,001 --> 01:35:54,334
<font color="#ffff80">We also checked
Sacred Heart Hospital</font>

1138
01:35:54,959 --> 01:35:56,793
<font color="#ffff80">and the Faculty of Medicine,</font>

1139
01:35:57,418 --> 01:35:59,709
<font color="#ffff80">but the person you describe...</font>

1140
01:36:01,043 --> 01:36:02,876
<font color="#ffff80">does not exist.</font>

1141
01:36:07,626 --> 01:36:09,209
<font color="#ffff80">Do you know what I think?</font>

1142
01:36:10,959 --> 01:36:12,626
<font color="#ffff80">You invented her</font>

1143
01:36:12,793 --> 01:36:14,876
<font color="#ffff80">because you're
weak and a coward.</font>

1144
01:36:15,543 --> 01:36:16,834
<font color="#ffff80">You invented her.</font>

1145
01:36:17,459 --> 01:36:21,459
<font color="#ffff80">Carla Miller gave you the courage to
kill your wife and keep her money.</font>

1146
01:36:28,209 --> 01:36:30,626
<font color="#ffff80">Get Forensics to
take away the body.</font>

1147
01:36:31,418 --> 01:36:34,751
<font color="#ffff80">And clear the road when you
can, this looks like a circus.</font>

1148
01:36:34,918 --> 01:36:36,751
<font color="#ffff80">Everyone, get out of here. Go!</font>

1149
01:36:36,918 --> 01:36:38,751
<font color="#ffff80">You heard. Everyone out.</font>

1150
01:36:39,251 --> 01:36:42,376
<font color="#ffff80">Call the judge. Tell
him we found the body</font>

1151
01:36:42,543 --> 01:36:45,626
<font color="#ffff80">and we can charge Ulloa
whenever he orders it.</font>

1152
01:36:54,418 --> 01:36:55,668
<font color="#ffff80">Get up.</font>

1153
01:36:57,626 --> 01:36:59,418
<font color="#ffff80">C'mon, get up. Let's go.</font>

1154
01:37:52,668 --> 01:37:54,084
<font color="#ffff80">Where are you going?</font>

1155
01:38:01,834 --> 01:38:03,293
<font color="#ffff80">I know.</font>

1156
01:38:04,209 --> 01:38:08,168
<font color="#ffff80">It's hard pretending to be
what you're not all the time.</font>

1157
01:38:08,334 --> 01:38:09,584
<font color="#ffff80">What's wrong with me?</font>

1158
01:38:09,751 --> 01:38:11,626
<font color="#ffff80">We've been at it eight
hours straight,</font>

1159
01:38:11,793 --> 01:38:14,251
<font color="#ffff80">shut in a goddamn morgue.</font>

1160
01:38:14,418 --> 01:38:16,209
<font color="#ffff80">How do you expect to feel?</font>

1161
01:38:16,376 --> 01:38:18,084
<font color="#ffff80">I need help. Please.</font>

1162
01:38:18,459 --> 01:38:19,876
<font color="#ffff80">Please.</font>

1163
01:38:24,751 --> 01:38:25,959
<font color="#ffff80">You know what?</font>

1164
01:38:28,168 --> 01:38:30,251
<font color="#ffff80">This reminds me of my wife.</font>

1165
01:38:31,918 --> 01:38:35,209
<font color="#ffff80">She died 10 years ago today.</font>

1166
01:38:40,918 --> 01:38:44,209
<font color="#ffff80">The official version is
that she had an accident.</font>

1167
01:38:44,959 --> 01:38:46,293
<font color="#ffff80">She was murdered.</font>

1168
01:39:06,168 --> 01:39:08,418
<font color="#ffff80">My daughter was in the car too.</font>

1169
01:39:13,959 --> 01:39:14,751
<font color="#ffff80">Are you okay?</font>

1170
01:39:14,918 --> 01:39:16,168
<font color="#ffff80">Yes.</font>

1171
01:39:18,584 --> 01:39:19,584
<font color="#ffff80">Ruth?</font>

1172
01:39:27,459 --> 01:39:30,668
<font color="#ffff80">A call to Emergencies
would've saved her life.</font>

1173
01:39:30,834 --> 01:39:33,376
<font color="#ffff80">But the car that
hit us drove off.</font>

1174
01:39:33,543 --> 01:39:37,293
<font color="#ffff80">I guess they were high
on some shit, or drunk.</font>

1175
01:39:37,626 --> 01:39:40,168
<font color="#ffff80">They left us there like dogs.</font>

1176
01:39:49,293 --> 01:39:51,584
<font color="#ffff80">Help! Help!</font>

1177
01:40:08,126 --> 01:40:10,168
<font color="#ffff80">She hung on for an hour.</font>

1178
01:40:10,709 --> 01:40:12,459
<font color="#ffff80">Ruth, my love...</font>

1179
01:40:13,418 --> 01:40:16,626
<font color="#ffff80">But she died a few minutes
before we were found.</font>

1180
01:40:22,001 --> 01:40:24,501
<font color="#ffff80">I tried to recall
the license plate.</font>

1181
01:40:25,626 --> 01:40:26,793
<font color="#ffff80">Nothing.</font>

1182
01:40:27,959 --> 01:40:30,668
<font color="#ffff80">Until, years later, my
daughter remembered.</font>

1183
01:40:35,293 --> 01:40:36,376
<font color="#ffff80">A hotel...</font>

1184
01:40:37,293 --> 01:40:39,168
<font color="#ffff80">...in Avalon,...</font>

1185
01:40:39,543 --> 01:40:41,709
<font color="#ffff80">...on the Island
of Santa Catalina.</font>

1186
01:40:42,959 --> 01:40:45,876
<font color="#ffff80">It was like looking for
a needle in a haystack.</font>

1187
01:40:46,459 --> 01:40:49,668
<font color="#ffff80">But I had all the time in
the world, and I found it.</font>

1188
01:40:57,418 --> 01:40:58,626
<font color="#ffff80">Drive.</font>

1189
01:40:59,876 --> 01:41:00,918
<font color="#ffff80">There's a little girl.</font>

1190
01:41:01,084 --> 01:41:03,293
<font color="#ffff80">- Did she see you?
- No.</font>

1191
01:41:04,001 --> 01:41:05,626
<font color="#ffff80">Then drive.</font>

1192
01:41:06,126 --> 01:41:10,626
<font color="#ffff80">How could you live all these years
knowing you were murderers?</font>

1193
01:41:13,084 --> 01:41:14,751
<font color="#ffff80">I want you to see something.</font>

1194
01:41:15,584 --> 01:41:17,334
<font color="#ffff80">It'll help you understand.</font>

1195
01:41:19,501 --> 01:41:22,793
<font color="#ffff80">My daughter. Her name's Eva.</font>

1196
01:41:24,668 --> 01:41:27,001
<font color="#ffff80">I won '1' be with you as
long as you're with her.</font>

1197
01:41:27,168 --> 01:41:30,543
<font color="#ffff80">We could have it all. She
could have an accident.</font>

1198
01:41:31,709 --> 01:41:33,501
<font color="#ffff80">Why won't you answer it?</font>

1199
01:41:33,668 --> 01:41:34,918
<font color="#ffff80">- Yes?
- Mr. Ulloa?</font>

1200
01:41:35,084 --> 01:41:38,293
<font color="#ffff80">This is Jaime Pefia. I'm
calling from the morgue.</font>

1201
01:41:39,001 --> 01:41:41,001
<font color="#ffff80">Your wife's body
has disappeared.</font>

1202
01:41:41,168 --> 01:41:42,751
<font color="#ffff80">What do you mean "disappeared"?</font>

1203
01:41:43,126 --> 01:41:45,501
<font color="#ffff80">It has to be more personal.</font>

1204
01:41:45,876 --> 01:41:50,376
<font color="#ffff80">Someone wishing to harm your
wife, even after she was dead.</font>

1205
01:41:50,793 --> 01:41:51,668
<font color="#ffff80">I'm in the car.</font>

1206
01:41:51,834 --> 01:41:55,043
<font color="#ffff80">I went out for a smoke. The
guard's still unconscious.</font>

1207
01:41:55,501 --> 01:41:59,084
<font color="#ffff80">We found a shovel and a sports
bag in the boot of Ulloa's car.</font>

1208
01:41:59,251 --> 01:42:02,126
<font color="#ffff80">In it are a balaclava
and some trainers</font>

1209
01:42:02,293 --> 01:42:05,543
<font color="#ffff80">that match the footprints on the
morgue 's emergency stairs.</font>

1210
01:42:07,918 --> 01:42:09,918
<font color="#ffff80">You were ready to
believe it all.</font>

1211
01:42:13,834 --> 01:42:15,168
<font color="#ffff80">Especially Carla.</font>

1212
01:42:16,501 --> 01:42:18,834
<font color="#ffff80">I just came out of
the restaurant.</font>

1213
01:42:19,126 --> 01:42:21,959
<font color="#ffff80">I left the mobile in the bathroom.
No one saw me.</font>

1214
01:42:22,126 --> 01:42:24,376
<font color="#ffff80">- What was that?
- The lift is stuck.</font>

1215
01:42:24,543 --> 01:42:26,376
<font color="#ffff80">We'll soon be together.</font>

1216
01:42:30,084 --> 01:42:31,084
<font color="#ffff80">Carla ?</font>

1217
01:42:32,751 --> 01:42:33,418
<font color="#ffff80">Carla!</font>

1218
01:42:36,126 --> 01:42:38,501
<font color="#ffff80">Eva got to you without
my knowledge.</font>

1219
01:42:38,668 --> 01:42:40,959
<font color="#ffff80">She feared the car she recalled</font>

1220
01:42:41,126 --> 01:42:43,251
<font color="#ffff80">didn't belong to her
mother's killers,</font>

1221
01:42:43,418 --> 01:42:45,876
<font color="#ffff80">that you and your
wife were innocent.</font>

1222
01:42:46,043 --> 01:42:48,084
<font color="#ffff80">I knew it was you.</font>

1223
01:42:48,251 --> 01:42:51,209
<font color="#ffff80">But she didn't, and she
wanted to be sure.</font>

1224
01:42:51,376 --> 01:42:55,293
<font color="#ffff80">The only way to verify your
guilt was to make you talk.</font>

1225
01:42:56,584 --> 01:42:58,084
<font color="#ffff80">She did it.</font>

1226
01:42:59,084 --> 01:43:02,418
<font color="#ffff80">You confessed your
darkest secret to her.</font>

1227
01:43:04,293 --> 01:43:06,793
<font color="#ffff80">Eva knew I was ready to act.</font>

1228
01:43:07,251 --> 01:43:10,918
<font color="#ffff80">She knew if she told me you'd
confessed to your crime,</font>

1229
01:43:11,751 --> 01:43:15,043
<font color="#ffff80">I'd have a green light to
go after you and your wife.</font>

1230
01:43:16,501 --> 01:43:17,793
<font color="#ffff80">And she did it.</font>

1231
01:43:17,959 --> 01:43:19,751
<font color="#ffff80">We have to do it, honey.</font>

1232
01:43:19,918 --> 01:43:21,709
<font color="#ffff80">She told me everything.</font>

1233
01:43:21,876 --> 01:43:25,126
<font color="#ffff80">Since then you've just been
a puppet in our hands.</font>

1234
01:43:26,459 --> 01:43:28,209
<font color="#ffff80">I know what you're thinking.</font>

1235
01:43:28,543 --> 01:43:31,043
<font color="#ffff80">Ten years leaves a lot
of time for thinking.</font>

1236
01:43:37,168 --> 01:43:38,876
<font color="#ffff80">The detective...</font>

1237
01:43:40,209 --> 01:43:42,043
<font color="#ffff80">...was a bargain.</font>

1238
01:43:42,209 --> 01:43:45,418
<font color="#ffff80">I just had to put the
invoice in the dossier.</font>

1239
01:43:45,584 --> 01:43:47,418
<font color="#ffff80">Eva and I took care of the rest.</font>

1240
01:43:47,876 --> 01:43:50,376
<font color="#ffff80">They also put a mike on you.
Listen.</font>

1241
01:43:50,543 --> 01:43:52,793
<font color="#ffff80">I've got everything. Mayka's
going to L.A. soon.</font>

1242
01:43:52,959 --> 01:43:55,668
<font color="#ffff80">It'll be when she comes back.
She hates flying.</font>

1243
01:43:55,834 --> 01:43:58,084
<font color="#ffff80">It'll explain the heart attack.</font>

1244
01:43:59,293 --> 01:44:01,043
<font color="#ffff80">Mayka knew everything.</font>

1245
01:44:01,626 --> 01:44:03,293
<font color="#ffff80">I'm at the airport.</font>

1246
01:44:03,459 --> 01:44:06,459
<font color="#ffff80">There's now no trace
of me you-know-where.</font>

1247
01:44:06,626 --> 01:44:08,334
<font color="#ffff80">Nobody saw me get here.</font>

1248
01:44:08,668 --> 01:44:10,251
<font color="#ffff80">I'm going back to Berlin.</font>

1249
01:44:10,959 --> 01:44:13,668
<font color="#ffff80">Javier Alonso is
conveniently on a trip.</font>

1250
01:44:13,834 --> 01:44:15,876
<font color="#ffff80">And of course, he didn't
find out anything.</font>

1251
01:44:16,043 --> 01:44:19,459
<font color="#ffff80">The only thing on record
is that Mayka hired him.</font>

1252
01:44:19,626 --> 01:44:22,709
<font color="#ffff80">I have your wife's body
and your confession.</font>

1253
01:44:23,418 --> 01:44:26,418
<font color="#ffff80">Nothing alters the
consequences of our actions.</font>

1254
01:44:27,126 --> 01:44:30,126
<font color="#ffff80">Sooner or later, someone
calls in the debt.</font>

1255
01:44:43,918 --> 01:44:46,209
<font color="#ffff80">You'll soon be joining her.</font>

1256
01:44:47,334 --> 01:44:49,126
<font color="#ffff80">- What's TH-16?
- A toxin.</font>

1257
01:44:49,293 --> 01:44:50,126
<font color="#ffff80">What kind?</font>

1258
01:44:50,293 --> 01:44:52,251
<font color="#ffff80">It's extracted from
certain reptiles.</font>

1259
01:44:52,418 --> 01:44:53,626
<font color="#ffff80">Why won't you answer it?</font>

1260
01:44:53,793 --> 01:44:54,668
<font color="#ffff80">Hello?</font>

1261
01:44:54,834 --> 01:44:56,918
<font color="#ffff80">Mr. Ulloa, this is
Inspector Jaime Pefia.</font>

1262
01:44:57,084 --> 01:44:59,001
<font color="#ffff80">I'm calling from the morgue.</font>

1263
01:44:59,543 --> 01:45:02,668
<font color="#ffff80">- Your wife's body has disappeared.
- What do you mean "disappeared"?</font>

1264
01:45:02,834 --> 01:45:06,043
<font color="#ffff80">Nothing tonight has
happened by accident.</font>

1265
01:45:06,209 --> 01:45:08,543
<font color="#ffff80">- Who was it?
- The police.</font>

1266
01:45:09,459 --> 01:45:11,543
<font color="#ffff80">I had a heart scare
two years ago,</font>

1267
01:45:11,709 --> 01:45:12,584
<font color="#ffff80">and I was fine.</font>

1268
01:45:12,751 --> 01:45:16,709
<font color="#ffff80">We've been at it 8 hours straight,
shut in a goddamn morgue.</font>

1269
01:45:16,876 --> 01:45:18,126
<font color="#ffff80">How do you expect to feel?</font>

1270
01:45:18,293 --> 01:45:19,543
<font color="#ffff80">Diluted in blood,</font>

1271
01:45:19,709 --> 01:45:23,709
<font color="#ffff80">it causes a cardiac 8 hours after
ingestion and leaves no trace.</font>

1272
01:45:45,334 --> 01:45:46,751
<font color="#ffff80">Tick-tock.</font>

1273
